&lt;p&gt;The role will be accountable for delivering analytical methods that are phase-appropriate and adhere to the highest scientific standards. The successful candidate must be able to collaborate in a fast-paced, integrated, multidisciplinary team environment. Research and industry experience should demonstrate successful application and management of state-of-the-art analytical techniques to solve problems, in addition to several years’ experience overseeing analytical development at CMO’s.&lt;/p&gt;
